{"tid":219371,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界級港女】41歲杜如風硬搶好姊妹男友 私會行街上香閨","createTime":"2017-04-27T07:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T03:49:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff6557b44516ee284f92fb291c4fb8f535f1883","tid":219371,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170427/large/1493264273_43d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170427%2Flarge%2F1493264273_43d6.jpg&h=fd956606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被封為「世界級港女」嘅杜如風，一直主持旅遊節目，帶住觀眾捐窿捐罅搵嘢食，不過由於佢亦好鍾意買嘢，講過自己有過千對鞋，又自稱走在潮流尖端(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/17zIHhg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F17zIHhg&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2ac50fff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/17zIHhg</a>)，41歲嘅杜如風感情世界似乎好dry(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pk5BUa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pk5BUa&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c026b621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pk5BUa</a>)，緋聞唔算多，最多人知就係佢同Shine成員黃又南拍過一年拖。<br />\n<br />\n今日有周刊就爆杜如風疑硬搶好姊妹Jenny嘅男友，Jenny係杜如風嘅御用化妝師，而Jenny有個拍拖多年嘅男友Alvin，不過今日有周刊爆杜如風同Alvin行得好埋，近月Alvin不時出入杜如風香閨，就連杜如風揸開嗰架波子，二人都兩份用，據知情者指杜如風同Alvin喺Jenny面前會保持距離，有時一齊出trip，杜如風同Alvin都玩得好癲，今年二月Alvin先同女友Jenny甜蜜慶祝生日，報道上月中就影到杜如風同Alvin私會，當時Alvin揸車送杜如風返去，二人上樓，Alvin幫佢撳門口密碼，上周四又見佢哋一齊返屋企，逗留4粒鐘，周一又去行街shopping，Alvin仲幫杜如風拎住晒啲戰利品，又不時扶實杜如風，翌日又再上杜如風屋企，見面都幾密，而好姊妹Jenny因為工作忙都冇懷疑。<br />\n杜如風剛才回覆《蘋果》先哈哈大笑，然後話：「笑料一宗，佢係我助手嚟!」之後佢又解釋：「女朋友係我好姊妹嚟，個女仔笑到死，話要澄清，個生日會唔係男友幫佢搞，係杜如風親自幫佢搞」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170427/56619425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170427%2F56619425&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c0bbdb2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170427%2F56619425&h=830f4fe4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170427/56619425</a>"},{"pid":"0586a551205c9aedd088bb60381aa7d4b606a166","tid":219371,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"我想食雪糕"},{"pid":"9420afc276f877e1b3b5f999ff050ec529d2199d","tid":219371,"uid":46086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想食雪糕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收皮啦，想上位"},{"pid":"fa391797f471d44c7be4d5483b3e1560fc01aa4e","tid":219371,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f548d593fee5452ac560914547b9d35b4c799004","tid":219371,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:39:36.000Z","msg":"香港公主"},{"pid":"d4c706744697873179f627fec595f41c9499763a","tid":219371,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a68d8dc12b51efac92811e53bb60a41891b442c","tid":219371,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}